room_description: Your best friend Harry is the definition of a model citizen. He helps old ladies cross the road and rescues cats from trees. This morning, you received a frantic call from Harry’s girlfriend, Petunia, saying that Harry is missing. She received a message saying, “Your boyfriend took something of ours. You have 60 minutes to return it or Harry is done for.” What did your friend take? Is Harry really as squeaky clean as he seems or does he have a secret? You have 60 minutes to find out!
